            "y1": 1365,
            "x2": 1688,
            "y2": 1501
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 13,
        "text": "विनिर्नीतंविमूढ़ेन कथंस्याद्देहकःपुमान् ।। ३४ ।।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_08_textline_13.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 313,
            "y1": 1492,
            "x2": 1870,
            "y2": 1650
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 14,
        "text": "चौ० । हे मूरुख सुन आतम जोहै ।। श्रुति युक्तिन करि",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_08_textline_14.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 292,
            "y1": 1737,
            "x2": 1976,
            "y2": 1872
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 15,
        "text": "वर्णित सोहै ।। देहातीत हेतु जग जोई । अति अदृश्य",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_08_textline_15.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 198,
            "y1": 1855,
            "x2": 1991,
            "y2": 1990
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 16,
        "text": "गुरु श्रुति कहै सोई ३० अहंशब्द करि जानौ जाहि । एक",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_08_textline_16.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 186,
            "y1": 1979,
            "x2": 1991,
            "y2": 2112
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 17,
        "text": "सर्बते परे सु आहि ।। देहस्थूल अनेक सु जोय । सो वह",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_08_textline_17.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 192,
            "y1": 2097,
            "x2": 1979,
            "y2": 2233
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 18,
        "text": "पुरुष सु कैसे होय ३१ हों द्रष्टा विषयादिक को पुनि । देह दृश्य",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_08_textline_18.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 186,
            "y1": 2211,
            "x2": 1982,
            "y2": 2349
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 19,
        "text": "यह ताहि जानि सुनि ।। मम यह देह ब्योहार सु जोय । पुरुष",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_08_textline_19.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 189,
            "y1": 2338,
            "x2": 1985,
            "y2": 2461
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 20,
        "text": "देह कैसे करि होय ३२ हों बिकार षट रहित सु जोई । देह सदा",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_08_textline_20.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 189,
            "y1": 2456,
            "x2": 1982,
            "y2": 2583
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 21,
        "text": "बिकार युत सोई ।। यह साक्षात प्रत्यक्ष प्रमान । कैसे होय सु",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_08_textline_21.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 189,
            "y1": 2574,
            "x2": 1979,
            "y2": 2707
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 22,
        "text": "देह पुमान ३३ सबते परे पुरुष है जोई । श्रुति तेहि लक्षण",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_08_textline_22.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 177,
            "y1": 2692,
            "x2": 1970,
            "y2": 2818
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 23,
        "text": "कहत सुजोई ।। ज्ञानिन करके बर्णित जोय । पुरुष देह कैसे",
